Package com.gemalto.mfs.mwsdk.mobilegateway.listener

Interface TransactionHistoryListener

public interface TransactionHistoryListener
Listener to return the transactionHistory for provided digitalCardId

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void onError​(String digitalCardId, MobileGatewayError mobileGatewayError)
    In case the request could not be fulfilled, this method will return the error object.
    void onSuccess​(List<MGTransactionRecord> transactionRecord, String digitalCardId, String timeStamp)
    MPA will receive list of transactions along with digital card id for which these transactions are performed.

  • Method Details

    • onSuccess

      void onSuccess​(List<MGTransactionRecord> transactionRecord, String digitalCardId, String timeStamp)
      MPA will receive list of transactions along with digital card id for which these transactions are performed. If API call is for Transaction Notification there will be only one Transaction record received. MPA should not save timestamp for Transaction Notification
      Parameters:
      transactionRecord - list of transaction records
      digitalCardId - the unique digital card id for which transaction history is requested
      timeStamp - time after which transaction history is requested, must be in format of ISO 8601 YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ssTZD

    • onError

      void onError​(String digitalCardId, MobileGatewayError mobileGatewayError)
      In case the request could not be fulfilled, this method will return the error object.
      Parameters:
      digitalCardId - the cardId for which refresh transaction history was performed
      mobileGatewayError - MobileGatewayError which contains errorCode, errorMessage and httpStatus
